{"tid":2030816,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港往何處去？ - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-05-23T04:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T05:32:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef495fd8a6d923975171c936e711176374e75218","tid":2030816,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:20:04.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200523/20922949/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200523%2F20922949%2F&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CKarsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=33828b7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200523%2F20922949%2F&h=d6c93fe7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200523/20922949/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港往何處去？ - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200523/large/1590138726_d523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200523%2Flarge%2F1590138726_d523.jpg&h=23db24b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《表姐，你好嘢！》截圖<br />\n<br />\n前天早上寫《頭條新聞》不合時宜，晚上人大就突然宣布，日內將表決通過一條在香港實施的法律。這條所謂國安法，至少有三大功能：一是確保黨能「依法」直接管轄香港；二是方便拘捕某些腰纏萬貫，從大陸跑來的「犯罪分子」（沒錯，即去年送中法秘而不宣的「初心」）；三是令港人疑神疑鬼，為免無端「犯法」而事事自我審查，名義上沒限制言論、集會等自由，但客觀效果就是全部都圈禁了。<br />\n<br />\n以第三點來說，《頭條新聞》諷刺政權，會不會令公眾對政府起反感呢？黨可能說「會」，即使實際是政府本身令人反感。令公。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相比起黨安法，我更關心那條被消失的歷史題和港台命運。香港是隻生金蛋的鵝，但金蛋不是我的，也不是你的，從來都是黨的。現在黨喜歡殺掉鵝，剁成肉絲，放進熱騰騰混雜果子狸、穿山甲、蠍子、蜈蚣肉。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港台今後何去何從呢？據中大傳播與民意調查中心去年的傳媒公信力調查，港台在電子傳媒中排名第二，僅次於Now TV。《頭條》腰斬，the show must go on，如何是好？昨天建議製作「藍絲」節目，並非說笑，比如做一個。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n香港是中國最後的奇蹟&mdash;&mdash;又屬於中國，又與國際接軌。至於港台，則是香港最後的奇蹟&mdash;&mdash;。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾<br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n精挑細味 籽想好食，即like「籽想好食」FB專頁！"},{"pid":"298bda28c474f22bc9ad0459cd1eed15a4ed1a99","tid":2030816,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T04:37:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7f572f5bd0dae05ec7e0f471ddca72f16280e05","tid":2030816,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T05:32:57.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}